        <abstract>
            <p>Condolences on JDH’s grandfather’s death.</p>
            <p>When his wife can move, they will go to Staffordshire.</p> 
<p>Returns some books; would like to see copy of <hi rend="italic">Kosmos</hi> [by Alexander von Humboldt]. Would be proud owner of JDH’s work [<hi rend="italic">Flora Antarctica</hi> (1844–7)].</p> 
